data.description: Discover a hidden gem! This recently renovated residence boasts three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, complete with a refreshing pool that demands your attention. Step inside to find elegant wood flooring seamlessly adorning every corner. The kitchen is a culinary dream, showcasing stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a stylish tile backsplash. The living room, adorned with a charming brick fireplace and a ceiling fan, exudes warmth and comfort. Each bedroom is equipped with its own ceiling fan for added convenience. The hallway bathroom features a shower over the tub, while the master bathroom offers a sleek shower stall. Venture outdoors to the inviting in-ground pool, surrounded by a gated area that provides ample space for delightful BBQ gatherings. Don't miss the chance to experience the allure of this exquisite home!
